Class NamingService

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.NamingService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObjectStore, TransactionsManager

    public class NamingService
extends java.lang.Object
implements ObjectStore, TransactionsManager
    TODO# Log should be trimmed. Need to keep a history of operations to trim properly. NamingService implements the object store interface to allow servers to broadcast availability.

    Is to be bootstrapped as the first process in charge of recording who is online.

    Only one naming service will be active at one time for now and will log all information it receives to ensure consistency.

    Defaults to port 10000 on localhost.

    See Also:
    RemoteObj, Clique, ObjectStore
